{"tid":755104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"厲害了我的國？「中國製造2025」偷消音 　變成這6字","createTime":"2018-07-25T02:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T05:52:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"eca0f137c1dc5faa332310267818ac5f275db19d","tid":755104,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"外界直指「中國製造2025」是觸發中美貿易摩擦的導火線，因此陸方近期開始刻意淡化，大陸工信部昨（24）日在新聞發表會上，罕見隻字未提「中國製造2025」，改以「製造強國建設」取代。<br />\n<br />\n2015年大陸國務院總理李克強提出「中國製造2025」計畫，對中國的工業現代化提出指引，希望藉此將中國從「製造大國」推升到「製造強國」，尤其電動汽車正是「中國製造2025」的重點產業。<br />\n<br />\n專家指出，美國發動貿易戰就是將矛頭指向「中國製造2025」，這個原本被大陸強力宣傳執行的國家戰略計畫，已被官方下令低調處理，不論是官方或陸媒的報導，「中國製造2025」幾乎已消失近1個月。<br />\n<br />\n工信部昨報告2018上半年工業與通訊發展情況時，首度對「中國製造2025」計畫隻字未提，僅以「製造強國建設」簡單帶過。當外媒追問，上半年報告中未提及「中國製造2025」，是否仍依原訂計畫執行？工信部發言人黃利斌並沒有正面回應，推測應是隱身檯面下。<br />\n<br />\n黃利斌表示，中國製造2025是本著開放發展、合作共贏的理念提出來的，目的是為中國製造業轉型升級提供戰略指引，並強調是在世貿框架下，制定和實施的戰略規劃，和美國等各國做法相同，歡迎外資企業積極參與，也希望外界能公正、客觀、理性看待中國製造2025。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180725000018-260410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180725000018-260410&d=URtt3CCGnuGnLRHpeOfLml0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6c58c4ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180725000018-260410</a>"},{"pid":"fa5d7269ce9004d8fbfa09e068eb6e17402c1622","tid":755104,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"2025 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee4d974664b8eb66d1ab453798965d536323ada","tid":755104,"uid":40369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:38:03.000Z","msg":"製造贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f159d97ec7d52f6661f570e218c069dcff68e87e","tid":755104,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國制造2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133e63ac417752c4fe45edfcf334a4e1e182fbf7","tid":755104,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"本港車站建設 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f72c5d9f55a48f9d331ef4e3e117c7fc4c346b","tid":755104,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"以為冇左年份侵侵唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa83cbc1715bf7141370542094e740e8387bad1","tid":755104,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國製造 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2025 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超越美國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong>"},{"pid":"01781affca6419c82302265042146ff1a5aa3d11","tid":755104,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"唔提姐，要偷嘅科技繼續偷"},{"pid":"44f8a9cd3be0c4bfb8b0ef4549bbfe33d7bc370e","tid":755104,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"改左名就冇人撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「製造強國建設」<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"4c23d41ca6bb786df6170fd1c567ac4d3b89211a","tid":755104,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\